    public class EnumMapBackedBijection<A extends Enum<A>,B extends Enum<B>>
extends MapBackedBijection<A,B,EnumMap<A,Bijection.Pairing<A,B>>,EnumMap<B,Bijection.Pairing<A,B>>>
    A specialized subclass of MapBackedBijection that uses EnumMaps as its backing Map type and maps enums to enums.
